<h1>FAQ</h1>

<div class="row">
    <div class="col-12 col-m-12 col-p-12 padding-0-20-0-20 ">
        <h2><b>How do I create an account?</b></h2>
        <p> 
            Click login to be directed to the login page. Then click New User Signup to create a new account.  
        </p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
    <div class="col-12 col-m-12 col-p-12 padding-0-20-0-20 ">
        <h2><b>Can I edit my username?</b></h2>
        <p> 
            Yes! Login to your account and navigate to the settings page. Once on the settings page there is a button to edit your suer name.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
    <div class="col-12 col-m-12 col-p-12 padding-0-20-0-20 ">
        <h2><b>How do I delete my account?</b></h2>
        <p> 
            Login to your account and navigate to the settings page. Once on the settings page there is a button to delete your account.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
    <div class="col-12 col-m-12 col-p-12 padding-0-20-0-20 ">
        <h2><b>Where can I see my energy usage?</b></h2>
        <p> 
            To see all the devices energy usage, simply navigate to the devices page. There is a table showing all of your devices, whether they are on or off, how much energy they're currently using and each devies average energy usage.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>

